        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Hokkaido/_scene_snowcrane.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 217286a9-beb9-4a7c-8473-775ab4e9d60e).Image",
        "Description": "Our client, an anonymous individual at the GAMA Medical Facility, has discovered the presence of several INTERPOL agents, likely attempting to gather information on illegal acts performed at the hospital and by its patients.\r\rThe ICA wants to avoid conflict with INTERPOL, so stay out of sight and ensure the deaths of these agents can be ruled as accidents.\r\rGood hunting, 47.",
